abstract: CINCINNATI, Aug. 4 (AP)--George Foster and Johnny Bench homered to help Tom Seaver make a successful return today as the Cincinnati Reds defeated the San Diego Padres, 7-1. The victory snapped San Diego's eightgame winning streak.
